description.plain: M24 is a rapper from Angel Town and member of Brixton group 150, a splinter of the former GAS gang. He first started making drill music in 2017, but burst onto the scene in 2019 with songs like We Don’t Dance and Verbal, and consistently created bangers throughout that year. He is also known for collaborating with artists like Tion Wayne, Skengdo, AM, and Unknown T.
